content.text:
I'll help you get familiar with this codebase. Let me start by exploring the project structure and understanding what we're working with.

<tool>
<Bash>
pwd
</Bash>
</tool>

<tool>
<Bash>
ls -la
</Bash>
</tool>

<tool>
<Bash>
find . -type f -name "*.json" -o -name "*.js" -o -name "*.ts" -o -name "*.md" -o -name "*.py" -o -name "*.txt" | head -20
</Bash>
</tool>

<tool>
Read>
package.json
</Read>
</tool>

<tool>
Read>
README.md
</Read>
</tool>

<tool>
Glob>
**/*.{js,ts,json,md,txt}
</Glob>
</tool>
